      <h1 class='title'>Northern Ireland Police Fund</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='lords-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HL Deb 01 November 2004 vol 666 c1WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1ws' title='Col. 1WS &mdash; HL Deb 01 November 2004 vol 666 c1WS' name='column_1ws' href='#column_1ws' rel='bookmark'>1WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0666P0-09546'>
        <a name='S5LV0666P0_20041101_LWS_1'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-valerie-amos' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0666P0_20041101_LWS_1' title='Link to this speech by Ms Valerie Amos' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-valerie-amos" title="Ms Valerie Amos">The Lord President of the Council (Baroness Amos)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S5LV0666P0-09546">My honourable friend the Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State for Northern Ireland has made the following Ministerial Statement.</p><p id="S5LV0666P0-09547">I have today placed in the library a copy of the report produced by John Steele CB OBE TD DL following his review of the Northern Ireland Police Fund. The Government accept the recommendations in principle and will work with the Police Fund on the implementation process.</p><p id="S5LV0666P0-09548">Copies of the report have been placed in the Library of both Houses.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
